title: Vote for Rumph in #ASunWBB Facebook Fan Poll
text: Atlantic Sun Facebook Fan Vote MACON, Ga. â€“ The Atlantic Sun wants to hear the fan voice for the 2015 Preseason Women's Basketball Awards. University of North Florida women's basketball's is up for Preseason Defensive Player of the Year. Fans can go to the Atlantic Sun's Facebook page to vote. The conference took the nominees for Preseason Player of the Year and Preseason Defensive Player of the Year from the A-Sun Coaches Preseason Ballots and has put the decision up to the fans. Winners of the fan polls will be included on the Preseason All-Conference Release on Thursday, Oct. 8. Voting is done by liking the player's photo. Deadline to vote is Thursday, Oct. 8 at Noon EST. Click here to vote for Rumph.
